Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_1_The_Third_Plate,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_2_Thirteen,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.82,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba Joichiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:13.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's... my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:26.04,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba-sama and Yukihira-kun... \Nfather and son...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:29.96,Italics Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Saiba-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:35.46,Italics Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}will{\i0} achieve a total \Nrevolution of this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:39.81,Italics Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,in order to save victims \Nlike you, Saiba-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:21.63,sign_1080_9_Totsuki,,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.92,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really going ahead with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.21,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,I've said it before... I'm not the \Ntype to make public speeches...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.83,Italics Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,Start talking, Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.34,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,If only Isshiki or Nakiri were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:30.47,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,And how much more time do \NI have before we go live?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.30,Main Dialogue,Nene,0000,0000,0000,,The cameras are already rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:33.06,sign_1451_15_Talk,Sign 0101,0000,0000,0000,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.06,Main Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:36.52,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hello. I'm Tsukasa Eishi from Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:40.99,sign_3800_20_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,539)}Advancement Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.48,sign_3753_19_Polar_Star__Dorm,Sign 0109,0000,0000,0000,,Polar Star\N Dormitory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.48,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here today to tell you all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.86,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,about the major event awaiting high-school
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.72,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,first-years at the end \Nof the second semester—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.36,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,the advancement exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.07,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, more than half of \Nthe first-years left the Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.28,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,due to the excessively rigorous exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.24,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on, that will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:57.72,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,Director Azami has liberated \Nyou from unnecessary weeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:01.19,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,You can easily pass most of the exam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:04.63,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,by demonstrating mastery of the\Ntechniques we have taught you in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:08.34,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,You are no longer bound by\N the old, outdated system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:14.23,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,If you side with Central, you can\N all become first-rate chefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:20.30,Main Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,But the exams will also clearly \Ndemonstrate what happens to those of you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.40,Main Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,who do not fall in line with \NDirector Azami's vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.49,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:28.41,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:31.62,sign_1080_9_Totsuki,,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:31.62,Italics Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, you or Kinokuni\N should do it, Rindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:32.79,Main Dialogue,Rindo,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:33.33,Main Dialogue,Nene,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The advancement exam, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Having it at the end of second \Nsemester sounds super early,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:40.73,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess we'll just have \Nto put our backs to it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.04,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,if we want to be second-years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.84,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.31,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why are y'all so glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.53,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you notice anything \Nabout what they said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:53.01,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Central basically declared us \Nrebels as targets in the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:56.28,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,That announcement was tantamount \Nto a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:04:00.47,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,It was a notice that anyone who does \Nnot obey Nakiri Azami will be expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.54,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.31,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, harbor folk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.90,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,You all sent me out to Tokyo for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.02,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I need to write a letter\N to the folks back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.78,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have such fond memories of the \Nfun we had at the camp from hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.37,Main Dialogue,Others,0000,0000,0000,,The camp from hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:18.32,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The Stagiaire we endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.68,Main Dialogue,Others,0000,0000,0000,,The Stagiaire...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.36,Main Dialogue,Ibu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.42,Main Dialogue Top,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The Moon Festival where we all came together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.67,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to get that depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.67,Main Dialogue Top,Others,0000,0000,0000,,The Moon Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:24.74,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.87,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,You should all write letters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:40.07,Flashback Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,The exams will also clearly demonstrate \Nwhat happens to those of you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.20,Flashback Dialogue,Tsukasa,0000,0000,0000,,who do not fall in line with \NDirector Azami's vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.11,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:48.15,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.33,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? You need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.75,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.38,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,About the match with Tsukasa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:17.60,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Any complaints you might have about my not \Nchoosing your dish are unfounded, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.43,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for taking on \Na match you couldn't have won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:24.15,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. I was outmatched,\N so that was a no-brainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.19,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What? F-Fine, as long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:32.58,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.93,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually here to talk \Nabout something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but sure, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:43.00,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Until a certain day, it may\N have been that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:50.26,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,No, I definitely did not have \Nany strong feelings about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:54.13,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,As someone with the God Tongue,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:57.20,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I was forced to face an overwhelming \Nnumber of dishes on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.86,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.67,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,No choice but to be disappointed \Nby what I tasted every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:08.40,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I met Saiba-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:13.65,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It was a short while after \NAlice left for Scandinavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:18.03,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That day, my taste-testing appointment \Nwas canceled, a rare occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:22.87,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,There were no other visitors, so I \Nremember it being very quiet at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.21,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.34,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:34.76,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.64,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.60,sign_7353_92_Hungry___,Sign 0508,0000,0000,0000,,Hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.34,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Erina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.57,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, Senzaemon-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.34,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what we agreed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:50.27,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,I only came because you said you'd \Nmake sure no one else would be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:54.86,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,My taste-testing appointment \Nwas canceled by the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.26,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:07:00.08,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Erina, this man is an old friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.62,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is a private meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:04.14,Flashback Dialogue,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.19,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.72,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.29,sign_8089_104_Hungry___,Sign 0528,0000,0000,0000,,Hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.30,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-chan, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.83,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.30,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Azami's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.99,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, you may stay and try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:21.60,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit lonely with just \Nthe two of us at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.89,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,There you go. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.15,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel a warm glow \Nspreading from deep within...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:44.04,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,This is totally different from \Nanything else I've ever eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.68,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:47.87,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.72,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.09,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,May I know your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.18,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,It's Saiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:10.95,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time I ever \Nthought food was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.31,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:15.23,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Never allow an imperfect dish to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.80,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Anything other than what I,\N your father, acknowledge is trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.63,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.82,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:25.20,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Six months later was when \NFather's "education" began.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:30.33,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I still remember the wonder I felt \Nwhen I ate Saiba-sama's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:35.96,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,But... I also understand where \NFather's principles are coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.88,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many imperfect \Ndishes in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:45.39,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up seeing the reality of \Nit for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:50.77,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore what food means to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:55.54,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very lost, not knowing what to believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:56.32,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.57,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.84,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I came here on an impulse,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.42,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,but of course I'm just bothering \Nyou by telling you all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.99,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.37,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.50,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you just need to taste \Nit one more time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.46,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:18.42,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Yukihira food for \Nyou right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.29,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a moment, Nakiri Erina-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.72,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:26.68,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:27.42,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.25,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.23,Main Dialogue Top,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.23,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Miss Secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.27,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.02,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find Erina-sama anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.93,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's using the \Nrestroom or taking a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.39,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I looked, but she wasn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.91,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Azami-dono may have abducted her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.84,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:41.19,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Azami-dono took her because I \Nlet my guard down for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:43.62,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,How could this have happened \Nwith me by her side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:46.87,Main Dialogue Top,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I could've prevented this with a body double\N or 3D printer or body-swap ninja technique—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.87,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's in Soma-kun's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:47.87,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:51.62,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have me taste \NYukihira food here right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:54.00,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,And what would that accomplish, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.49,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The dish Saiba-sama prepared \Nwas wonderful beyond comparison
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:59.27,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,to the likes of your crude creations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:02.51,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're not all meek anymore!\N You're back to your normal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:06.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dad trained me hardcore at home, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:11.48,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll remember something if \Nyou taste some Yukihira food, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.39,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:16.28,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you planning to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,A tempura bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.65,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,A tempura bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.39,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.99,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you taste something \NI'm really proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:28.43,Main Dialogue,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He totally just made that face he makes when\N he's about to create something grotesque!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.49,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of tempura are you \Nplanning on making, Yukihira-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.05,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to serve that to the God Tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.67,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,If her sensitive palate were to \Nmeet one of Yukihira's grotesque dishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:39.84,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst case scenario, death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.05,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:47.14,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun's preparing a dish because he has \Nsomething he wants Nakiri-san to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.64,Main Dialogue,YR,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:51.09,Italics Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing you say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:53.62,Italics Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,...as someone who's fallen victim \Nto his grotesque dishes the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.85,Italics Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,You've got zero credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:57.31,Italics Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:58.77,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.61,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Bonito's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.32,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Batter's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.57,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I already had some rice soaking,\N so that was lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:11.12,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll serve up an unbelievably \Ntasty tempura bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:16.29,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira Soma, you look just \Nlike you did that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:20.35,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,when you were facing the Elite Ten's\N first seat, Tsukasa Eishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.19,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Despite challenging an insurmountable wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:26.80,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,you still looked like you were having \Nan incredible amount of fun cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:32.88,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I looked like that \Nwhen I was little, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:37.44,Flashback Dialogue,Adults,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama, you have a responsibility \Nto the Nakiri family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:42.40,Flashback Dialogue,Adults,0000,0000,0000,,Please prioritize the\N family name over your own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.49,Flashback Dialogue,Adults,0000,0000,0000,,That's the God Tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.86,Flashback Dialogue,Adults,0000,0000,0000,,I should curry favor with her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.24,Flashback Dialogue,GirlAlice,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Erina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:53.65,Flashback Dialogue,GirlAlice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the top chef \Nat Totsuki Academy some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:57.95,Flashback Dialogue,GirlAlice,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be really fun \Nto perfect the dishes I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.45,Flashback Dialogue,GirlAlice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to hold back \Njust because we're cousins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.03,Flashback Dialogue,GirlAlice,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it our best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.92,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.89,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:13.35,Flashback Italics Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think cooking's fun at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.52,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking depressed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.62,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're usually all high and mighty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but you sometimes get like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.15,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.21,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Perk up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:30.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm super stoked that \NI can finally get back at you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.45,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,for what happened the day we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.37,Flashback Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.75,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:46.63,Flashback Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you say "delicious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:53.51,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day I'll make \Nyou say "delicious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.36,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.84,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You have confidence, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.93,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What dish could you have \Npossibly prepared for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.09,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:12.85,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Yukihira-Style Chicken's Egg Tempura Bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.81,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken's egg tempura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.60,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.19,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:21.31,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The egg white is barely set,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:23.15,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,and the yolk is perfectly soft-boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.61,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's silky smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.59,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.92,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,So he made raw egg tempura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.28,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,How did he even fry it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:34.41,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just chuck a raw egg into\N hot oil to get a tempura egg, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.54,Main Dialogue,Ibu,0000,0000,0000,,The batter wouldn't stick \Nto it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.67,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Did he fry it inside its shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.54,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Is she supposed to eat it shell and all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:44.80,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Did he batter and fry a\N soft-boiled egg, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:48.39,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,No, the heat would've fully cooked the yolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.55,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,How did he make this dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.80,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.40,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.06,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You're as irritating as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:59.52,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The secret's inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.36,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You took the egg from the freezer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.12,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:06.86,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This tempura was made by coating \Na frozen raw egg with batter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.82,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's the star of this tempura bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:11.83,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Peel a frozen egg, dip it in batter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,then fry it up nice and crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.91,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Drizzle a good amount of sauce \Non freshly-made piping-hot rice,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:21.31,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,pair the egg tempura with fried perilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.68,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,pour more sauce on top,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:23.34,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.17,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:30.76,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,But novelty foods don't impress me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:35.33,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,A dish with egg as its main\N ingredient will be simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.82,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That means the chef's skills \Nand the ingredients' quality
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.60,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,are directly reflected by the dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.82,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hope you won't regret serving \Nthis dish to the God Tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.63,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Erinacchi's gonna taste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:50.13,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I wonder if it's up to snuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.17,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:56.58,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,I actually saw Yukihira-kun \Nmaking a bulk purchase earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.55,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Of bargain eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.08,sign_19341_266_Bargain_Eggs,Sign 1330,0000,0000,0000,,Bargain Eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:00.08,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,Sold for 106 yen a dozen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.18,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What, bargain eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.43,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:08.59,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Since infancy, Erina-sama has been surrounded\N by only select, high-quality ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:13.60,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows how her body might react\N if she were to taste something {\i1}cheap{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.06,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.27,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Erinacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.85,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.10,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell right away
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:35.95,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,that the egg you prepared is different \Nfrom those of high-class silky fowl
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.74,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,and other brand name eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:41.21,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,This egg is of the same quality as those \Nserved at the common kitchen table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.67,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It should be a far cry from refined cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.76,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.97,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:58.43,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,How is it even possible to achieve...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:03.90,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,such delicate and complex... flavors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:11.10,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,About how freezing changes the egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.91,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's another advantage to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:18.12,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It intensifies the flavor of the yolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.50,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The flavor... intensifies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:26.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Freezing chicken eggs causes the proteins \Nto coalesce into a gel-like state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:29.92,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That results in a creamy, \Ngelatinous mouthfeel,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:33.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,and a much richer yolk flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.76,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, freezing the egg
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:38.56,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,is the single most important \Ncontributor to this dish's taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.24,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's also a generous amount
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:43.73,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,of a sweet-and-spicy umami sauce, \Na Yukihira special blend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:47.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strongly-flavored sauce with a \Nbonito stock base, soy sauce, and mirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.90,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question that it pairs \Nwell with the egg and rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:54.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But if you used an egg \Nthat's too rich in flavor,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.49,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,the overall dish would become overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.83,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:04.61,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The frozen egg's mouthfeel and richness, \Nplus the special sauce's strong flavors—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:08.84,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to use a lighter-tasting \Negg to maximize the two components!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.84,sign_19341_266_Bargain_Eggs,Sign 1539,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(260,1)}Bargain Eggs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:09.84,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:13.19,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,So he chose bargain eggs for a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.68,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Soma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.18,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:19.64,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,eggs were the topic you assigned back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:26.64,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this is the perfect dish \Nto settle our score once and for all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.91,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:30.44,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.43,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,How did you even come up with this idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:36.35,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's common knowledge that \Nfreshness is key to egg quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:39.85,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, isn't it the norm \Nto focus on obtaining the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.83,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,rarest and highest-quality eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.75,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, how did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:44.98,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come up with this—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:46.66,Main Dialogue Top,S,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.60,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.80,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think people who \Nonly know one "correct" answer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:55.17,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,can get themselves to reach \Neven greater heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, above all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:03.82,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how did you come up with those \Ncombinations of ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.48,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Each dish was so innovative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.20,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Unconventional, yet meticulous...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:11.23,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know from the start that \Nthe dish will turn out well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.57,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.68,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.13,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I test a new dish,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.70,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 50 percent certain and\N 50 percent taking a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:22.95,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,Even today, several dishes were \Nusing your gramps as a test subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.91,Flashback Dialogue,GirlE,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you go so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.37,Flashback Dialogue,Jo,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:30.00,Flashback Dialogue,Jo/S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If you know exactly where \Nyou're headed, it's no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:30.00,Main Dialogue,Jo/S,0000,0000,0000,,If you know exactly where \Nyou're headed, it's no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.21,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:34.92,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:37.59,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.81,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,...wanted to do {\i1}that{\i0} kind of cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.27,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.90,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Erina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:04.41,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Only dishes I acknowledge and Central \Ncreates can be considered food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.16,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:08.33,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,Eradicating all else as \N"feed" from the Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.10,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,and nurturing the entire \Nstudent body into a loyal army
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.59,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,will strengthen Totsuki as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.29,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.22,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}I{\i0} advance as true gourmet food
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.76,Flashback Dialogue,Azami,0000,0000,0000,,will become absolute justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.47,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:23.63,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Father, I believe the \Nchefs and their dishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.64,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,want to be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:35.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.78,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,How was the Yukihira special?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:42.41,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's hear it for the taste, Nakiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.62,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It was delicious, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:45.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.04,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:51.75,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.56,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.16,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Do exactly what I'm about to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:57.80,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.36,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow morning at seven o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.80,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Have all the Polar Star Dormitory \Nfirst-years assemble before the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.59,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me, but how was the taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.19,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.03,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.01,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,What about the taste?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:13.14,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:21.11,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Tadokoro-san that she can dispose \Nof the letter she was writing home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:22.99,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.45,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.95,sign_27250_374_The_Next_Morning,Sign 1858,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(563,1)}The Next Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.23,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,Brr...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.33,Main Dialogue,Ibu,0000,0000,0000,,It's technically winter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:38.98,Main Dialogue,Maruki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we won't have much longer to \Nbreathe in the morning air at the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:41.09,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives are over once the \Nadvancement exam happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:44.77,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Nakiri-san wants, \Ngathering all of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.47,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she didn't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:48.93,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.27,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Erinacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.21,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.12,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Good day, Polar Star Dormitory residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:57.81,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.13,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.19,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You all look dejected again, like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.40,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.76,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious now what the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:07.53,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,outcome of the advancement exam would be,\N before it even happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.66,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'd be better for all of you \Nto just leave the academy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.18,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:13.91,Main Dialogue,Aoki,0000,0000,0000,,You had us all show up just to tell us that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:19.02,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We all want to keep on cooking \Nat this academy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.27,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.64,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:28.27,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,It's been some time since I came \Ninto this dormitory's care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:32.22,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, I have sampled \Nyour creations numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:36.23,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,At times, they tasted unusual.\NAt other times, they tasted absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.73,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost count of how many times \NI scolded you all for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.94,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,But your dishes were always free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.68,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay down like you are now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:52.96,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,you will be terminated without even \Ngetting to build on your strengths!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:53.89,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:55.29,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really how you want things to end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:59.42,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,B-But how can we pass the exam, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:01.63,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question about how!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.84,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to get through it \Nwith the power of your cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.09,Main Dialogue,Marui,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:08.63,Main Dialogue,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,She's starting to sound like Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:10.09,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:18.03,Flashback Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I've started to think about \Nwhat I really want to do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:23.57,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the determination \Nto survive this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:27.53,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I will support you using everything I \Nhave in my power as the God Tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.98,0:22:30.74,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have the willpower \Nto survive, then just leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:34.91,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Those who stay will face the exam with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:36.40,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:39.04,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,If you are true chefs with any pride at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:41.99,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.96,sign_30623_420_Totsuki,,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:10.97,sign_30671_421_Food_Wars,Sign 2121,0000,0000,0000,,Food Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:10.97,sign_30671_422_The_Third_Plate,Sign 2121,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:10.97,sign_30671_423_Next_Episode__On,Sign 2121,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode  {\fs16}Onward on the Totsuki Train
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:09.66,Main Dialogue,Sign 2121,0000,0000,0000,,Hop on that train, and go, go, go!
